            <h2 class="fw-bold">About PneumoTrack</h2>
            <p>
                <span class="highlight">PneumoTrack</span> is a machine-learning based web application designed to assist in the detection of <span class="highlight">pneumonia</span> through chest X-ray images. 
                Pneumonia, a severe lung infection, affects millions worldwide and can be fatal if not diagnosed promptly. Our application leverages the power of <span class="highlight">deep learning</span> 
                models to offer a fast, accurate, and reliable way to detect pneumonia from X-ray scans.
            </p>
            
            <h5 class="mt-4">Why PneumoTrack?</h5>
            <p>
                In the wake of the COVID-19 pandemic, pneumonia detection has become more critical than ever, as the virus can lead to severe lung infections. 
                Accurate and early detection of pneumonia is essential to improve patient outcomes, especially in regions with limited healthcare resources. 
                <span class="highlight">PneumoTrack</span> aims to bridge the gap by providing quick diagnosis with a focus on accuracy and efficiency.
            </p>

            <h5 class="mt-4">How It Works</h5>
            <p>
                Using the latest in <span class="highlight">Convolutional Neural Networks (CNN)</span>, <span class="highlight">PneumoTrack</span> analyzes chest X-rays to detect signs of pneumonia. 
                The model was trained using a publicly available dataset from <span class="highlight">Kaggle</span>, consisting of over 5,000 labeled X-ray images of pneumonia cases and normal lungs. 
                The model, once it detects pneumonia, automatically generates a report and emails it to the patient, helping in faster diagnosis and treatment.
            </p>

            <h5 class="mt-4">Key Features</h5>
            <ul>
                <li>AI-driven pneumonia detection using chest X-rays</li>
                <li>Detailed reports delivered via email for both patients and healthcare providers</li>
                <li>Integration of modern web technologies for a smooth user experience</li>
                <li>Real-time analysis with high accuracy</li>
            </ul>

            <h5 class="mt-4">Aiding the Medical Community</h5>
            <p>
                <span class="highlight">PneumoTrack</span> not only speeds up diagnosis but also helps reduce the workload on radiologists and diagnostic centers by offering an automated solution. 
                This allows healthcare professionals to focus on treatment, rather than spending excessive time diagnosing.
            </p>

            <h5 class="mt-4">The Future of PneumoTrack</h5>
            <p>
                As we continue to evolve, we aim to incorporate new features such as severity classification, additional lung condition detection, and even providing treatment recommendations based on the detection. 
                Our mission is to make pneumonia detection accessible and accurate, benefiting both patients and healthcare professionals alike.
